{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96f92767",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ここで逢ったが百年目！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.3",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "96f92767",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ちょっとこっちに来てくださいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52846a6a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……ちょ！？　な、なんだよオイ！　腕引っ張るなって！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f30fdf3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いきなり飛び出すように現れた雫。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.0",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8d27d5d6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫は俺に有無を言わせず、腕を掴むと部屋の中に引っ張り込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.0",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ddada235",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "何なんだよホント……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "28d34ec2",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "お話があります……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "47.0",
      "line_index": 47,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2fb35ed9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "は、話……？　だったらなんでわざわざ部屋に引っ張り込む必要が……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.0",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "50c3f9a7",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "うるさいですね……！　ほかの方に聞かれても少し困ることなので……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.4",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "50c3f9a7",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "話と言うのはこの前の……キッチンでのことです……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "55.0",
      "line_index": 55,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "55bf9b2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "キッチン……？　ああ、雫が手コキを──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b524357a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それ以上言わないでくださいっ！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.2",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b524357a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わたくしにとって人生の最大の汚点なのですからっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.0",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "320dff22",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、汚点って……それ酷くないか？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.2",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "320dff22",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そもそもあれは雫の方から襲ってきたわけだろっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ccd5aa11",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "違います……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.3",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "ccd5aa11",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あれはその……惚れ薬を間違えて飲んでしまって、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.5",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "ccd5aa11",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それであんなことを……本心ではなかったのですっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.0",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d3adc3e2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "惚れ薬！？　な、なんでそんなもの……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.2",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d3adc3e2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "というかあのジュースにそんなもの入れてたのかよっ。なんでだよ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "48603aa2",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "そ、それは……あなたなどにお話しする必要はありませんっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "15261cf1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "惚れ薬のことは今はどうでもよいのです。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.4",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "15261cf1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それよりもあなたがヘンな勘違いをしていないか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.6",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 6,
      "line_hash": "15261cf1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それが気がかりで……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f7a5bd0",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わたくしには心に決めた方がいるのだから、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.2",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5f7a5bd0",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あの時の出来事はなかったことに……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.6",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 6,
      "line_hash": "5f7a5bd0",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "できれば記憶から抹消してほしくて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87b80d94",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そんなことできるわけないだろっ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.2",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "87b80d94",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "結構、その……すごかったし……記憶に焼き付いてしまったというか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "385a13f1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "お、思い出さないでっ！そもそもあなたがヨワヨワなのが原因なんだからっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6014289a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あの程度で……どれだけザコなのですか。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.4",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "6014289a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あんなザコよわよわおちんちん、仮に挿入されたとしても、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.6",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 6,
      "line_hash": "6014289a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わたくしなら１ミリも感じないでしょうねっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75d6d756",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……む！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cab2b907",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "な、なんですかその顔？　カチンときましたって言いたげですね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9a2053d8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そりゃ言いたい放題言われたら、ムっとするだろ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.2",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9a2053d8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……雫の言葉が本当かどうか試してもいいんだぞ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f399d208",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ふふん、強がって……なら試してみますか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.4",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "f399d208",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あなたのざこざこ租チンじゃ絶対に感じませんからね、ほほほっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5990d7a3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "売り言葉に買い言葉、どちらも引くに引けなくなる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.0",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "682f5588",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして俺達は何を思ったのか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.2",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "682f5588",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "互いに下着を脱ぎ捨てると性器を見せあう形になってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.0",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4035b39d",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ふ、ふん……相変わらず貧弱……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.0",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4c60ffe5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の肉棒をまじまじとみつめる雫。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "90df7882",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺は仕返しとばかりに雫の閉じた割れ目をじっとみつめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e3dab9a3",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "見ているだけで何もしないつもりなの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.4",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "e3dab9a3",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あなたっておちんちんだけじゃなくて、心もよわよわなのねっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5fbfb063",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫は俺を挑発するように脚を拡げると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.2",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5fbfb063",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "割れ目をぐいっと指で開く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.0",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a487e4f8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思わぬ形で雫の綺麗なピンク色のあそこを見てしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.2",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a487e4f8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "興奮が高ぶっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e93a6a83",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こ、後悔するなよ？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.2",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e93a6a83",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もうここまでされたら俺止まらないぞ？　いいんだな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "430d4ec",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ふん……！　あなたこそ後悔しないことね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.2",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "430d4ec",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "もう二度とその粗末なモノが大きくならないくらいメタメタに──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.0",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "978359a3",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "──はうっ！？　う、うぐぅ！　う、う……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.2",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "978359a3",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "い、いきなり……なん、てぇっ……この卑怯者ぉ……ぐうっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "507b4413",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺は雫がすべてを言い終わる前に、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.2",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "507b4413",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "カウンターのように陰茎を膣穴に押し込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.0",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "88a242a2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "急に挿入され、歯を食いしばり挿入に耐える雫。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8e95e1ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな雫に心が痛むものの、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.2",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8e95e1ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "男としての意地を見せるように肉棒を押し込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "878f3c8f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "う、く……ふ、ふ……ほら、こんなの全然たいしたことないですわね。はははっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.2",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "878f3c8f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わたくしの見立て通り……あなたはざこざこのよわよわ……っ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "78df7edb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "その言葉、絶対に後悔させてやる……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.2",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "78df7edb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "雫を感じさせまくってやるからな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.4",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "78df7edb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "アヘアヘさせてやる、覚悟しろよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.0",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fc50c1c",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ふん、出来もしないこと言わないでっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "90e828e0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うあ……なんて狭さなんだ……でもここで引くわけにはいかない……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.2",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "90e828e0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あそこまで言われて引き下がれるか……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1edea5e0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ピストンをすると、肉棒を押し返すように膣中が締まる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "358c0801",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒でこじ開けるように膣中を押し広げる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "92befa04",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何度もピストンを繰り返しているうちに、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.2",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "92befa04",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しっとりとしていた膣中が愛液で満たされ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.4",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "92befa04",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "トロトロになっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.0",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4e17d551",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ふっ……ふっ……ふふ、ん……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.2",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4e17d551",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "や、やはり、大したこと……んっ！　ありませんね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.0",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e6e1c152",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "こんなへたくそな腰振りで……くっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.2",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e6e1c152",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "女を感じさせようなんてお笑いですっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.0",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a48c159",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "さっきから減らず口を……おまんこ濡れてきてるし、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.2",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5a48c159",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "感じてるの丸わかりなんだぞ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
